Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.07,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何も怖くなんてないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.68,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手にしたものを失うくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:51.42,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}争いを待つ事を繰り返して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.92,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かすめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何もかもを欲しがっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迷えるものの誓い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:05.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未だ見ぬ世界を創りだす事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.57,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}朽ち果てていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:15.58,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}哀しい夢を遮るものは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.37,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自らの闇だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.93,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.26,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.43,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.60,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Makes me feel何処からか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.36,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}流れる景色変わらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.28,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}音もなく解き放つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.10,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}畏れ断ち切り何時からか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.24,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}高鳴る鼓動止まらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.48,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}易しくも消し去って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.07,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我並非是在膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.68,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去曾經的擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:51.42,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}等待著周而復始的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.92,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}掠奪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}曾經渴求著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}立下極易迷失的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:05.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必將創造出人們從未見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.57,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直至此生的終結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:15.58,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}阻擋哀傷之夢的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是自身的迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.93,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.26,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.43,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.60,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Makes me feel會有一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.36,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}變幻之景不再更迭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.28,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悄然間將自身解放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.10,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}切斷畏懼後不知從何開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.24,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}內心的悸動無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.48,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻又輕易地將其熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:16.62,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向かい風吹く 一寸先 予想も出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一心不乱 キミに付いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.75,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一期一会の宝を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:29.07,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}足が震えても 止まらない 胸の高鳴り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.97,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}前人未到 旅はいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.00,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全身全霊 エンジン全開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:40.97,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絶対キミを守る どんなリスクがあるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.58,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}‘絶対'なんかないさ チカラを尽くそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:55.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思い切り吸い込んだ 果てしない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Star the space-time trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.68,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}望遠鏡覗けば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.44,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}カリスマティックな闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}うねる波の迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(365,330)}ラビリンス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:15.92,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Never stop! 幽閉された星を解き放つため
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}キミと旅立とう 月が明日へ導く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(375,330)}あす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:16.62,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迎風而立 未來無法預料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一心一意 追隨在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.75,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誓取一生的珍寶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:29.07,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}即便腳步顫抖不已 也難阻心中的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.97,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}前无古人 隨時啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.00,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全心全力 火力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:40.97,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絕對要保護你 無論艱難險阻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.58,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凡事沒有絕對 但會竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:55.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}徹底掉入無盡的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Star the space-time trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.68,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}從望遠鏡中看去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.44,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充滿誘惑的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}曲曲折折的迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:15.92,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Never stop! 解放幽閉之星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與你同行 月引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:06.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來 人們就對妖怪心存畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:12.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而走在那眾妖之前 統領著百鬼夜行的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:16.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們稱其為妖怪的總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:18.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是如此稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魑魅魍魎之主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑頭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 怎麼了 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 好美的月亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:11.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:16.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣平安地過著每一天真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去打架的好天氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:19.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:31.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸生決意包容造反的牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:41.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過陸生尚未察覺 在西方刮起了不安定的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,300)}魔鏡來襲 吞食果實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:03:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做那個夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從6歲開始一直重複的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:24.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天明明是我的生日 卻糟糕地醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:33.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那個奇怪的夢害我沒睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:43.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 你才6歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼長大了再來一起玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:52.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦 我會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:53.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島同學真不愧是U-14日本代表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來幫忙 青田坊…不是 倉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也謝謝冰麗前來加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 像這樣 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別覺得不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是可以保護自己不被妖怪傷害的愚歩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是面向超級初學者的版本哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:34.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:38.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都為了你們好 還想全裸時被襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 家長同學也來學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:54.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實應該最先學會的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很容易被妖怪盯上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跟著做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 大家都在練習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在做愚歩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍天白雲下 修行陰陽護身術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美妙的青春之頁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 新的妖怪體驗大會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:27.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家長同學 今天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一家人 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛快快地收下禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼 裡面有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這盒子好像是名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛…詛咒人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是把家長同學妖怪化的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:03.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 超可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這可是特別訂做的高級商品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼無聊的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:11.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了 清繼同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我今天先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不參加發表會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我有點睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩把這個搬回教室了 你們可以先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:26.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要先準備晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:35.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 少主就交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:39.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以回來得太晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:42.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:54.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能收到生日禮物很高興 不過這實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:02.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在你生日那天來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽說過紫之鏡的故事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫之鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 妖怪雲外鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通稱紫之鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也叫照魔鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:25.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一眼這個鏡子就會被詛咒 並且在13歲生日那天被殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站有這麼遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殺掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是13歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:42.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來 在妖怪的世界裡13歲是成人年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說成人了就會被殺掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 因為已經成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人又不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 奴良同學 你來晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在打掃教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 加奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你13歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:28.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 我來接你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:34.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈來一起玩吧 繼續7年前的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊 從夢裡出來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩躲貓貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 愚歩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鏡子裡玩躲貓貓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:24.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我明明是往車站走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:27.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼會到學校了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫色的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:48.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 你才6歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:51.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼長大了再來一起玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:56.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦 我會來接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:01.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你13歲生日那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:09.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 這個房間沒有鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狹窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狹窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雲外鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:22.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒聽說過 但應該是被哪個組開除的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 今天是加奈的生日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:30.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對 關於剛才的生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我還準備了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:33.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是把我妖怪化的可愛的人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出不來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡…鏡子 又要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:13.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚了吧 其實這人偶裡裝了移動電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是清十字團的通信器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:26.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 現在我被怪物 從鏡子裡出來的怪物襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:30.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 現在你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校的某個男廁所裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:39.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個男廁所？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:04.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學你們找那邊 我找這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:12.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清繼同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看不見我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:25.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人來哦 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:32.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸…陸生同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能看到這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡只屬?我和加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:46.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 被吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:12.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混球 別在我的地盤上對女人動手動腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:19.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來…別來妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:29.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 不知道哪個才是真身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:30.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不知道 那全砍了就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:01.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:05.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在這邊 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪兒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家長同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:12.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是我搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:21.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點睡眠不足 在迷糊時看到了這個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:40.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被老鼠妖怪抓住的時候 合宿的時候 現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次只要有陸生同學在 你就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:52.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:57.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 再多陪我一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再告訴我一些你的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算留下可怕的回憶也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:22.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 害怕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:33.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和你在一起 什麼都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很想知道我的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會完全告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:20.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到妖怪和風餐館化貓屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:22.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺像樣的嘛 幹得不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我好了 我已不會再出錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:37.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說少主 這女孩不是被舊鼠抓走的人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她來這種地方真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:45.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 良太貓 交給你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不能小看少主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟帶來了位這麼可愛的情人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:56.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說他被稱作少主 看來這個人真的是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:09.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12…不 今天就13歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是生日？那真是恭喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:21.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說今天就成人了 真是太可喜可賀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為一個出色的妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你是什麼妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:27.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他們知道你是人類 一會兒會吃掉你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 呐 到底是什麼妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 我要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡…鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:48.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:52.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人偶好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪兒買的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:08.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的世界原來是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟想像的有點不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:22.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊 這孩子也是妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…少主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各種妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽喝足了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜品店婆婆的料理水平真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主真是的 都這個時候了還不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:53.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「少主就交給我好了」 竟然把少主跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓先生 木天蓼果汁真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 能玩得盡興真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙招待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:26.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 陸生是早上才回來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這孩子很行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我在做什麼啊 怎麼做出了昨天那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:46.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 少主 昨天晚上你去哪裡做了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:49.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加…加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上抱歉了…啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:54.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:59.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 陸生同學 我有點事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:02.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要問什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:15.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了想之前到現在的行動 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有陸生同學那個人就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:25.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道陸生同學和那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 要穿幫了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 告訴我關於那個人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:40.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然我不是很明白 為什麼想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:46.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不行的啊 跟陸生同學又沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 還沒開始營業
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:10.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三郎貓 你的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才突然刮起的風弄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 只不過衣服破了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:35.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是衣服壞了？他還真是什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來奴良組的幼稚是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來偵察真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴良組的根據地浮世繪町
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:50.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮壓這個街道所需要的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多一星期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:30.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個領子好緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢 阿青
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:34.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領子上的扣子不是都解開的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:35.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個季節你還圍圍巾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:36.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 滑頭鬼之孫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:40.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西風打頭陣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
